      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality F80-generation M3, featuring the S55 3.0L twin-mono-scroll turbocharged inline-six mated to a 7-speed M-DCT. This specimen is mechanically flawless, retaining its original factory-honed adaptive M suspension and active M differential for optimal lateral grip and torque vectoring. The CFRP strut tower brace remains unblemished, and the forged light-alloy wheels are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. With a comprehensive service history and zero modifications, this vehicle offers a pure, factory-spec driving experience. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or trim degradation.",
