    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, mirror-like gloss with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather retains its original matte finish and scent, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of every service record from day one. It has been pampered with preventative maintenance and only the highest quality fluids. All electronics function perfectly, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
